Syntax: wear <object>
Syntax: wear all

Wear is used to equip yourself with an <object>.  There are some objects
you can not wear in combat but you will be able to disengage to wear them.
Wearing an object can add command lockout and can add a period where the
wearer can not hit in combat.

See also: REMOVE, WIELD, EQUIPMENT
Related Topics: OBJECT MANIPULATION
